claim: Joaquin Phoenix campaigns for Bernie Sanders.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Other groups involved in organizing this conference include Democratic Socialists of America , Food & Water Watch , Our Revolution  (  previously the Bernie Sanders presidential campaign , 2016  )  , People Demanding Action , People 's Action , Progressive Democrats of America , Reclaim Chicago , United Electrical , Radio and Machine Workers of America , United Students Against Sweatshops , Million Hoodies , and African-Americans for Bernie Sanders .
